text: Hazel Greene-Pereira is an Irish archer. She was born on 19 November 1960. Greene competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics, 1984 Summer Olympics, and the 1988 Summer Olympics.Hazel Greene-PereiraHazel GREENE-PEREIRA == References == Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Irish archers Category:Olympians for Ireland
